name: I Did Time at the D.O.C. - Short Sleeve T-Shirt by CleanWear
description:
Doing time at the D.O.C. is never a good thing unless you're doing it at the One & Only D.O.C. store in Longmont, CO!

D.O.C. is the flagship store of CleanWear and is THE place where Art and Fashion Find Purpose. We commit a percentage of all CleanWear Prison Artwork apparel sales to 2nd second chance programs to help people get on and stay on the right track in life.

D.O.C. of Longmont, Colorado has built a solid reputation of having unique clothing and artwork for those wanting to set themselves apart. With a top notch staff and great selection of products for every look, D.O.C. is where everyone flocks to keep looking their best and support great causes!

D.O.C. t-shirts are made in the U.S.A. with ultra soft 100% cotton. Our water-based inks leave a soft-hand feel on these black t-shirts.

Pick one up today and let everyone know that YOU did time at the D.O.C.!
